---
title: Salmon and Gremolata Butter with Broccoli Puttanesca
description: Gremolata -- a sauce of freshly chopped parsley, zingy lemon zest and garlic - is paired with butter to create the ideal accompaniment to pan-fried salmon. It's served with a simple, savoury broccoli puttanesca.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salmon-and-gremolata-butter-a1d50367.jpg
